title: Leah Roberts // 26
description:
Most of us have thought about escaping our everyday lives in search of adventure. But after a young woman from North Carolina takes off on a road trip by herself without telling anyone her plans, her car is found wrecked on a backroad in Washington state and she's nowhere to be found. This is the disappearance of Leah Roberts.
